### Bojang Backend API Testing
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
# @baseUrl = https://your-service.onrender.com

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Authentication - Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "username": "testuser",
    "password": "testpass123",
    "displayName": "Test User"
}

### Authentication - Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "testpass123"
}

### Get Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/content/categories

### Get Levels
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/content/levels

### Get Questions for a Level (replace level-id with actual ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/content/levels/level-id/questions

### Get User Progress (requires authentication)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/progress/user
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Submit Quiz Session (requires authentication)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/progress/quiz-session
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "levelId": "level-id",
    "results": [
        {
            "questionId": "question-id",
            "userAnswer": "answer",
            "isCorrect": true,
            "timeTaken": 5
        }
    ],
    "totalScore": 100,
    "accuracy": 1.0
}

### Get Achievements
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements

### Get User Achievements (requires authentication)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/achievements/user
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Weekly Leaderboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/leaderboard/weekly

### Get Monthly Leaderboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/leaderboard/monthly

### Test Static File - Image
GET {{baseUrl}}/media/images/animals/cat.jpg

### Test Static File - Audio
GET {{baseUrl}}/media/audio/animals/khyi_dog.wav

### Sync Data (requires authentication)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sync/upload
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "quizSessions": [],
    "gameScores": [],
    "achievements": []
}

### Get User Profile (requires authentication)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Update User Profile (requires authentication)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "displayName": "Updated Name",
    "preferredLanguage": "en"
}
